        "a": "Most of the major platforms are US-only and do not support Canadian bank accounts, provincial tenancy rules, or CAD currency. Revun is built for both US and Canadian landlords, which makes it one of the few options that works cleanly if you own properties on either side of the border or plan to expand into both markets."
